---
// src/components/CustomHero.astro
---
<section class="relative min-h-[60vh] md:min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center px-6 w-full mb-8 mt-4">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    
    <div class="transition-all duration-1000 ease-out opacity-100 translate-y-0">
      <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm tracking-[0.3em] text-black/50 dark:text-white/50 uppercase mb-8">
        深海 · 峨眉 · 过去来的人
      </p>

      <h1 class="font-sans text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-black dark:text-white leading-[1.1] mb-8 min-h-[1.2em]">
        <span>探求 AI 的</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--primary)]">边界</span>
        <span class="inline-block w-[4px] sm:w-[5px] md:w-[6px] h-[40px] sm:h-[48px] md:h-[60px] bg-black dark:bg-white align-middle rounded-sm ml-2 -translate-y-1 animate-pulse"></span>
      </h1>

      <blockquote class="max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">
        <p class="text-black/60 dark:text-white/60 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed italic">
          「我不知道我在想什么，直到我读到我写的东西。」
        </p>
        <footer class="mt-2 text-sm text-black/40 dark:text-white/40">—— Flannery O'Connor</footer>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="#post-list" class="group flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3 bg-black dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-black rounded-full font-medium text-sm hover:opacity-80 transition-all duration-300">
          浏览文章
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/about/" class="px-8 py-3 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-full font-medium text-sm text-black dark:text-white hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-all duration-300">
          关于我
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute -bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
    <div class="w-px h-12 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/20 dark:from-white/20 to-transparent relative">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)] animate-bounce"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>